{"tid":2342261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（廢老kol 燒山）港名嘴搭高鐵脫口罩錄影「滔滔不絕18分鐘」　遭檢舉違規成疫情破口","createTime":"2020-12-27T03:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T01:51:20.000Z","uid":237459,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0891344afc7cc16f5bf2eb83749697e8ece118c2","tid":2342261,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"最近紐籍機師引發航空器群聚與台灣零本土個案破功，民眾多少重新意識到防疫態度鬆懈不得，以免產生破口。讀者王小姐昨（12/26）向《蘋果新聞網》投訴，在Youtube看到香港名嘴蕭若元前天（12/25）發布兩支影片，場景看來都在高鐵車廂內，拍攝過程他均未戴口罩。此舉已明確違反指揮中心明令搭乘雙鐵須全程配戴口罩的規定。高鐵規定旅客乘車須全程戴口罩，除非有飲食需求，且鄰座無人或隔壁乘客配戴口罩，才可短暫飲食；即使鄰座無人，仍不可脫下口罩乘車甚至拍影片或直播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201227/NHSKXCZHMZH6JICPRSKGF56BWY/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR20JgK4Yl42trSNP3Vl3psoNQa55OmToAUZonQpB46y51pyNL12YDbp32w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201227%2FNHSKXCZHMZH6JICPRSKGF56BWY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR20JgK4Yl42trSNP3Vl3psoNQa55OmToAUZonQpB46y51pyNL12YDbp32w&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=9c55543f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201227%2FNHSKXCZHMZH6JICPRSKGF56BWY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR20JgK4Yl42trSNP3Vl3psoNQa55OmToAUZonQpB46y51pyNL12YDbp32w&h=af8298d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201227/NHSKXCZHMZH6JICPRSKGF56BWY/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR20JgK4Yl42trSNP3Vl3psoNQa55OmToAUZonQpB46y51pyNL12YDbp32w</a>"},{"pid":"d1c815bb65864862c627f9f126acc078e4d85118","tid":2342261,"uid":41873,"like":3